description:
A simple and lightweight VPN over socks5 proxy (tun2socks) A simple and lightweight VPN over socks5 proxy for Android. It is based on a high-performance and low-overhead tun2socks.

Features

  • Redirect TCP connections.
  • Redirect UDP packets. (Fullcone NAT, UDP in UDP/TCP)
  • Simple username/password authentication.
  • Specifying DNS addresses.
  • IPv4/IPv6 dual stack.
  • Global/per-App modes.
